{"arkId":"cl010113458","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113458","modified ":"2025-10-31","title":"Th\u00e9i\u00e8re du service Demidoff","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Th\u00e9i\u00e8re du service Demidoff"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Restauration (1814-1830) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1817","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 560 - Claude Ott, Acc\u00e8s r\u00e9serv\u00e9","room":"Salle 560, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1817,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"1e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Odiot, Jean-Baptiste-Claude","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"08\/06\/1763","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"23\/05\/1850","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q3176320"},{"label":"Cavelier, Adrien-Louis-Marie","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"D\u0027apr\u00e8s","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 12166","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"orf\u00e8vrerie, argenterie ; th\u00e9i\u00e8re","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"La th\u00e9i\u00e8re est orn\u00e9e, sur une face, d\u2019un bas-relief montrant Bacchus accroupi, couvert d\u2019une peau de b\u00eate et tendant une grappe de raisin \u00e0 une panth\u00e8re dont il tient une patte, et sur l\u2019autre face, d\u2019une L\u00e9da allong\u00e9e avec un cygne, une draperie flottant au-dessus. L\u2019encolure est cisel\u00e9e d\u2019une frise de rinceaux de vigne, de roseaux et de dauphin, identique \u00e0 celle du pot-\u00e0-oille. L\u2019anse en nacre, coup\u00e9e par une bague \u00e0 fleurettes, se raccorde par des attaches \u00e0 feuilles d\u2019eau. Le couvercle plat est somm\u00e9 d\u2019une prise en cygne sur un nid de feuilles et de fleurs.\r\nArmoiries grav\u00e9es sur le couvercle.\r\n\r\nLe 15 f\u00e9vrier 1817, Odiot fournit au comte Nicolas Demidoff (1773-1828) un service \u00e0 th\u00e9 en vermeil \u00e0 manches de nacre, comme l\u0027attestent les archives de la maison Odiot.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Fabricant (J.B.C.O., un soufflet de forge) (\u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle et au revers)\r ; Moyenne garantie (au revers, \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle et au bord du pied)\r ; Paris, argent, 1809-1819, 1er titre (au revers et \u00e0 l\u0027int\u00e9rieur du couvercle)\r ; Signature : \r ; J.B.(TE).C.(DE) \/ ODIOT  (\u00e0 lint\u00e9rieur du couvercle et au revers)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Profondeur","value":"15","displayDimension":"15 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"17,5","displayDimension":"17,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"28","displayDimension":"28 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : vermeil = argent dor\u00e9\r\nMat\u00e9riau : nacre","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Nicolas Demidoff (1774-1828) ; son fils, Anatole Demidoff (1812-1870) ; probablement vendu \u00e0 la maison Hancock en 1863, et achet\u00e9 par Joseph-Xavier-Alfred de Morton, comte de La